2015-12-14 - Sam

Minimum functionality:
1. Tools to connect in real time to external data sets
2. Tools to test relationships between some external factor and asset price changes that signal an actionable opportunity
3. Monitors that look for tested signals in the external data and take action
4. A means of selecting the best of available opportunities to act on to optimise scarce capital
5. A way of keeping score for each model to see if they need to be turned off or moderated
